  "title": "TLM Smartstream Consultant",
  "description": "<p><strong>TLM Smartstream Techno-Functional Consultant</strong></p><p><strong>Responsibilities</strong></p><p>• Development and configuration of solutions utilizing smart stream TLM Application suite including TLM Control, TLM Smart studio, TLM Recon admin, TLM View, MI to support enhance and develop the platform<br />• TLM Solution config and implementation working with users/project team to design, build, test and deliver the solutions<br />• Create and maintain documentation<br />• Execute the unit testing, system integration & user acceptance testing<br />• Configuration/code management and maintenance of dev/test environment<br />• Follow the delivery governance model and regular updates to project & Business stakeholders</p><p><strong>Mandatory Skills</strong></p><p>- 3-8 years of relevant experience with TLM 2.4 & TLM 3.0<br />- Good knowledge of a RDBMS in particular at least one of Oracle, Sybase & SQL Server.<br />- Good knowledge of at least two operating systems including Windows, Unix, and/or LINUX<br />- Has solid solution configuration/ implementation skills including the ability to configure business applications using front end tools, database table updates, and data transformation tools (ETL).<br />- Strong experience in smart stream TLM Application suite including TLM Control, TLM Smart studio, TLM Recon admin, TLM View, MI to support enhance and develop the platform<br />- Have worked on TLM Solution config and implementation working with users/project team to design, build, test and deliver the solutions<br />- Experience in unit testing, system integration & user acceptance testing,<br />- Writing test case, test design and configuration/code management and maintenance of dev/test environment<br />- Good communication skills and stakeholder management</p>",
